{"tid":2199470,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"茶記廢中會引全國民調話侵侵十一月輸硬, 因為佢地唔知咩叫推舉人票","createTime":"2020-09-12T08:39:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T11:58:35.000Z","uid":76115,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0469d343dc7bb24aa2914051ea3bb4b82c218313","tid":2199470,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T08:39:39.000Z","msg":"美國政治呢，係睇州份的。<br />\n你輸推舉人票，全國民調以至得票畀你納哂都沒用。<br />\n自從侵侵喺ＤＮＣ演講爆紅之後，佢啲州份民調爆能到牙媽都唔認得。<br />\n民主（極左共產）黨連第一修正案槍權都唔認，要在美國呢挺以革命送君主上斷頭台立國嘅地方贏，我真係笑咗。<br />\n<img src=\"http://s01.geekpic.net/di-FWME4E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs01.geekpic.net%2Fdi-FWME4E.png&h=82a520f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45bbf3e6b80506975f5eef4bb91f792aca019f94","tid":2199470,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T08:43:40.000Z","msg":"樓主假膠"},{"pid":"ae5601f21f3ca207da273f05aecc9939cd7de709","tid":2199470,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T08:44:27.000Z","msg":"第二修正案 同獨立宣言"},{"pid":"8fe19a32263e348341781f580831e2d27d910551","tid":2199470,"uid":76115,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T08:45:28.000Z","msg":"贏哂啲<strong><span class=\"red\">O</span></strong>州。我地侵侵，十一月，贏到「<strong><span class=\"red\">O</span></strong>」哂嘴。<br />\n<img src=\"http://s01.geekpic.net/di-77OUAW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs01.geekpic.net%2Fdi-77OUAW.png&h=36fd611d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/50/23/00/502300df8f539c98f687831a1316438f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F50%2F23%2F00%2F502300df8f539c98f687831a1316438f.gif&h=330c3136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://nnimgt-a.akamaihd.net/transform/v1/crop/frm/3AijacentBN9GedHCvcASxG/d0c1b8be-ee01-462a-8085-1e70ba97d387.jpg/r0_176_1101_798_w1200_h678_fmax.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h